<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q26_v7" title="Q26_v7" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Una empresa de catering cobró $96 000 por servir 24 platos de fondo y $56 000 por servir 14 postres.</p>
    <p>Se sabe que el cobro es proporcional al número de platos servidos. Si en otro evento se sirven x platos de fondo y x postres, ¿cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa el costo total, en pesos, de ese evento?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>96&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mn>24</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>56&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mn>14</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El costo por plato de fondo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>96&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos y el costo por postre es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>56&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>14</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos. Si se sirven <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> platos de fondo y <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> postres, el costo total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4000</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4000</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8000</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>, que equivale a sumar ambos costos unitarios y luego multiplicar por <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>96&#160;000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>56&#160;000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión usa <m:math><m:mn>96&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mn>56&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> como si fueran costos unitarios, pero son costos de 24 platos de fondo y de 14 postres, respectivamente. Por ejemplo, si <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, esta expresión da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>96&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>56&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>152&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos, mientras que el costo real es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>96&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>56&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>14</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>96&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>24</m:mn>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>56&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>14</m:mn>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En esta expresión <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> queda en el denominador, por lo que el costo disminuye cuando <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> aumenta, y eso no representa una relación proporcional directa con la cantidad de platos. Por ejemplo, si <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, esta expresión da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>96&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>56&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos, pero el costo real debe ser <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8000</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>96&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mn>24</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>56&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mn>14</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Aquí solo se multiplica por <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> el costo de los platos de fondo, pero no el de los postres. Si <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, esta expresión da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4000</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos, mientras que el costo real es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4000</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4000</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular el costo de un plato de fondo</strong></p>
            <p>Como $96 000 corresponden a 24 platos de fondo, el costo por cada plato de fondo es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>96&#160;000</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>24</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Cada plato de fondo cuesta 4000 pesos.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el costo de un postre</strong></p>
            <p>Como $56 000 corresponden a 14 postres, el costo por cada postre es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>56&#160;000</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>14</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Cada postre cuesta 4000 pesos.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Expresar el costo de x platos de fondo y x postres</strong></p>
            <p>Si se sirven <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> platos de fondo, su costo es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Si se sirven <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> postres, su costo es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Sumar ambos costos</strong></p>
            <p>El costo total del evento es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8000</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 5: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa A representa exactamente:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>96&#160;000</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>24</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>56&#160;000</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>14</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8000</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión correcta es la alternativa A.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>